<plot>Three young men, dripping bravado, stand by their cars at the top of a long curved road, challenging each other to a race. One wants it to be for pink slips. Off they go. Each has a bag of tricks, and each must negotiate surprising developments, including the sudden appearance of another car and then a lightning storm. Who will win, and what price victory?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?500169</url></doc>
